{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a9adc96845","title":"广西省临桂县饿死五百三十一人","origin":"新华通讯社编《内部参考》1955年7月21日","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9466bf6d6b","index":0,"year":1955,"month":7,"day":16,"articleId":"a9adc96845"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7f99454ee3","name":"郭纯青"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4daae7d9f9","type":"title","text":"广西省临桂县饿死五百三十一人","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9adc96845"},{"id":"351408fd88","type":"authors","text":"郭纯青","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9adc96845"},{"id":"ac04741b02","type":"paragraph","text":"【广西分社十六日讯】广西省桂林专区临桂县，由于粮食统销问题没有彻底解决，在七月二日前，已饿死五百三十一人，身体浮肿的达六千人。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9adc96845"},{"id":"a33b28bc09","type":"paragraph","text":"整顿粮食统销工作后，临桂县领导上麻痹大意，没有进行深入检查，各地统销量太产，每月大人十多斤，小孩几斤，米吃完了，吃野菜，以致中毒浮肿而死。现在当地农民生产情绪很低。中共桂林地委获悉后，已调拨大批粮食进行救济。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9adc96845"}],"page":{"id":"99638c07b6","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a9adc96845","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}